title: Andreas - Quintos
description:
I could swear that I've seen this here before... but it's not here now, so....

--------------------------------------------------------

Quintos

Darguad/Long Currier, 2005ish, 55 pages  

Story by Andreas

Art by Andreas and Isa Cochet

Spain, 1937. The war between Spanish nationalists and republicans rages. Volunteers from all over Europe have joined the republican troops to defend democracy and fight against the fascist threat that corrupts all. A poignant and deeply human story which brings an innovative vision of war through the strife, the madness and the suffering it usually generates
